{"tid":2040933,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港股警號】吉利10.8元低殘配股：將來充滿不確定性之動態挑戰","createTime":"2020-05-29T02:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T04:03:17.000Z","uid":61257,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d694c5436f17f6ff3dbae48484d1a4d74c709981","tid":2040933,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"吉利汽車（175）突然宣佈，以每股10.8元配售6億股，佔擴大後股本6.11%，集資淨額64.47億元，每股作價較前收市價折讓7.85%。大股東李書福持股量將由43.88%降至41.2%。消息拖累吉利股價急跌10.4%，報10.5元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吉利董事認為，面對於可見的將來充滿不確定性之動態挑戰，配售股份集資並同時拓闊其股東及資本基礎提供機會。董事認為，配售將增強吉利之財務狀況及為提供營運資金。<br />\n<br />\n作為藍籌股的吉利配股，亦拖累港股整體港股氣氛，恒指低開351點，惟其後跌幅收窄至139點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錢都要賣啦!</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200529/3IUU5QM4LFAGFTEBTPBEXLNSFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200529%2F3IUU5QM4LFAGFTEBTPBEXLNSFE%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=9640d76b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200529%2F3IUU5QM4LFAGFTEBTPBEXLNSFE%2F&h=ed6219c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200529/3IUU5QM4LFAGFTEBTPBEXLNSFE/</a>"},{"pid":"2443a76c3e8b0b32e1173313d1a2e75f5d0e147e","tid":2040933,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:07:06.000Z","msg":"大騙子愛康健呢？"},{"pid":"9f0ef7c458ebb0461cbb6512d9360ce0d5499022","tid":2040933,"uid":162478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"吉利靈車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買得中資股，升先係唔正常"},{"pid":"3714f88388aa995e10e0d6cf19ee3dd9149eb93b","tid":2040933,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2443a76c3e8b0b32e1173313d1a2e75f5d0e147e","tid":2040933,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:07:06.000Z","msg":